{"tid":589871,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[實驗] 每日只食兩餐","createTime":"2018-03-12T06:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T01:01:42.000Z","uid":123335,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"cd2dfe7e5e9d97f60089572879909bced5037bac","tid":589871,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T06:59:28.000Z","msg":"今朝早餐 9點食 <br />\n<br />\n份量如下 : <br />\n卡路里: 800kcal <br />\n碳水化合物: 110g <br />\n蛋白質: 26g <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時未覺好餓  <br />\n兩餐之間只係飲水 / 淡茶 (普洱) <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時感覺幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9add6ab07a710459c93049d24f64618e328cc022","tid":589871,"uid":5843,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:01:42.000Z","msg":"屌，見到都覺得好撚肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831cef8d972eede6272eff45386b70724b5b1002","tid":589871,"uid":156331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:06:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2bde325e3d704f130c1c55a5781a9a97f4b0d014","tid":589871,"uid":123335,"like":4,"dislike":14,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:14:30.000Z","msg":"動機 (Motivation) : <br />\n點解要食兩餐  ? <br />\n<br />\n1. 省錢 : \b我果區食Lunch 閒閒地都 $45 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 省時間 :  出去食lunch 要時間 , 食lunch 要時間 , 食完 lunch 消化緊會飯氣攻心要時間 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 減肥 : 減少卡路里攝取 , 從而控制體重 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 提神: 飢餓感引發動物生存既原動力 , 振奮精神"},{"pid":"185be72e302ce38df79dea648f086c4cec535692","tid":589871,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"831cef8d972eede6272eff45386b70724b5b1002","tid":589871,"uid":156331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:06:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:15:24.000Z","msg":"綠茶寒涼 , 空肚飲對胃部刺激性大阿ching"},{"pid":"73d673d6289fd808c75474c17e321c2b40bf11bc","tid":589871,"uid":123335,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:18:58.000Z","msg"